_sText:
Map aim_stalker_arena - arena map from the game S.T.A.L.K.E.R. Shadow Of Chernobyl

This map is perfect for a 1x1 or 2x2 battles (but can be more).

Map as close to the original atmosphere of the game as possible.

At the map is present arena ambient (taken directly from the game).

Just, on the map there is an audience and Arnie himself (arena organizer).

Map is well optimized for mobile version CS:Source.

Map transferred completely me (SaViMoN).

Thank you for your attention!
